==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Duboisine
<hw>Du*bois"ine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>An alkaloid obtained from the leaves of an Australian tree
(<spn>Duboisia myoporoides</spn>), and regarded as identical with
<altname>hyoscyamine</altname>. It produces dilation of the pupil of the
eye.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ducal</ent>⟦br⟧
